latestIgtvVideos.title: @doctor.amir.md appreciation post!!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
To everyone curious about my LASIK surgery here is a little (edited) clip on how it went. I got procedure done at @eyephysiciansoflongbeach with the best @doctor.amir.md! Whole process in the OR took less than 30 minutes with actual laser “drilling” my eye for only 15 seconds (you can hear/see it towards the end of the clip). Recovery was very fast - went home, slept and next morning I was fine. I even drove myself to my post op appointment 😁 if you ever considered doing this surgery - don’t wait any longer!!!! My only regret is - why I haven’t done it sooner?? Best decision ever!
P.S.: it’s really IMPORTANT to request LISA!! Lisa is the coolest nurse that helped me with all tests and made this experience super smooth ❤️

Thank you guys so so much!!
